{"id":"addar","term":"Addar","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Ample, splendid, son of Bela (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 8:3\">1 Chr. 8:3</a>); called also “Ard” (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 46:21\">Gen. 46:21</a>)</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 8:3","Genesis 46:21"]}